{"tid":289080,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人成日自己睇豪宅相幻想？","createTime":"2017-06-18T16:23:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-18T17:23:52.000Z","uid":6503,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"215d900aefd51211c133d872f0431532d61c3c72","tid":289080,"uid":6503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T16:23:06.000Z","msg":"唔知道身邊朋友係唔係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n我成日會上網睇下豪宅啲相 內部裝潢 幻想下如果自己係住係入面可以有幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n並不是講緊下面呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/19/001855_dbc11b2b774b33087e6484b9c335fcdc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F19%2F001855_dbc11b2b774b33087e6484b9c335fcdc.jpg&h=27bb4fd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/19/001939_8e41269cc261a15e659732e44e40e834.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F19%2F001939_8e41269cc261a15e659732e44e40e834.jpg&h=d510ad5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢啲一棟棟有乜好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  要睇就睇呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/19/002108_c7ee9edf5962cba3a87d2ecdc088d266.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F19%2F002108_c7ee9edf5962cba3a87d2ecdc088d266.jpg&h=03d3f940&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/19/002152_ea0d8f647443dd15a0bddeee4e186f1a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F19%2F002152_ea0d8f647443dd15a0bddeee4e186f1a.jpg&h=13e37a1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/19/002216_be5a26b13d53bbf798f8c2c8b92cf009.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F19%2F002216_be5a26b13d53bbf798f8c2c8b92cf009.jpg&h=da615346&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n靚到痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  係咪可能我太窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  得我先會咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62b39cf0652194cc5656b75b819bbf25514652d7","tid":289080,"uid":6503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T16:24:12.000Z","msg":"無人會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"5f20953d34edd58191c424d92ff3038b99367160","tid":289080,"uid":6503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T16:26:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"871511efdcbf47b8be436bf4a48961c343185a29","tid":289080,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T16:27:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> on9"},{"pid":"f83cbc18a37cfa8abd7c2edc4d18406dbf6ff50c","tid":289080,"uid":6503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T16:29:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> on9</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但ff下都好"},{"pid":"0e831526acc1a0d76ea146868421ed5be2eba80e","tid":289080,"uid":54812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T16:30:05.000Z","msg":"玩the sims嘅目的就係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eef400d98c0323e5cdaf820b4be29ca2739352fc","tid":289080,"u